phrases.localized: Aparthotels are hotel-like accommodations with rooms that feel more like apartments. They usually have a front desk, hotel-like amenities, and staff available to assist guests.

phrases.description: RYS: Label for the Apartment property type category

phrases.localized: Dammusos are stone houses with wide walls and domed roofsan architectural style unique to the island of Pantelleria in Italy.

phrases.localized: Nature lodges are professional hospitality businesses located in natural settings like forests and mountains.

RYS: More detailed description of the Chalet property type
phrases.localized: Chalets are houses that are usually made of wood and have a sloping roof. Many are holiday homes in locations popular for skiing or summer homes.

phrases.description: RYS: More detailed description of the Serviced apartment property type
phrases.localized: Serviced apartments are furnished and serviced by professional management companies. They offer hotel-like amenities such as daily cleaning, laundry service, concierge, and a front desk, making them popular choices for corporate housing and guests staying longer than 30 days.

phrases.description: RYS: Name of the Apartment property type category

phrases.localized: A loft is a spaceusually an apartment or condowith an open layout. Most or all walls in a loft do not extend fully to the ceiling.

phrases.description: RYS: More detailed description of the Island property type
phrases.localized: An island is a piece of land completely surrounded by water. Islands are great for private getaways in paradise.

phrases.description: RYS: More detailed description of the Pension property type
phrases.localized: Pensions are Korean holiday homes often found in the countryside. They often have barbeques and other communal spaces that make them a good choice for groups and families.

phrases.description: RYS: More detailed description of the Windmill property type
phrases.localized: Windmills are unique structures originally designed with blades to catch the wind and use its energy. Some windmills may be fully functioning while others are primarily used as living spaces.

phrases.localized: Houses are residential buildings that are often stand-alone structures. Some houses, like duplexes, may share walls or outdoor areas with other houses.

phrases.description: RYS: More detailed description of the Lighthouse property type
phrases.localized: A lighthouse is a tower with a bright light originally built to help ships navigate waterways. Theyre usually found on the coast near large bodies of water.

phrases.description: RYS: More detailed description of the Train property type

phrases.localized: Barns that have been converted into living spaces may have been originally used for storing grains, livestock, or farming equipment.
